Package: dsJobsClient
Type: Package
Title: DataSHIELD Client for Durable Federated Job Runtime
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Sarrat González", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "david.sarrat@isglobal.org"),
    person("Juan R", "González", role = "aut", email = "juanr.gonzalez@isglobal.org"))
Description: Client-side DataSHIELD package for composing and orchestrating
    durable federated jobs. Provides generic step constructors for session-plane
    (DataSHIELD assign/aggregate) and artifact-plane (allowlisted subprocess
    runners) operations. Jobs are submitted as immutable specs, executed durably
    on hospital nodes, and return disclosure-safe results. Domain-specific DSLs
    (radiomics, imaging, preprocessing) live in upstream packages and compile
    down to generic dsJobsClient jobs.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    DSI,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr,
    DSLite
Config/testthat/edition: 3
